 Naturally, we'll charge different prices for different sizes.

00:04:00.820 --> 00:04:03.320
 Then for third-breads, we'll have to charge a lot extra.

00:04:03.320 --> 00:04:04.520
 Oh, sure.

00:04:04.520 --> 00:04:06.820
 They need a more delicate soap.

00:04:06.820 --> 00:04:09.020
 Homer, do you know what else we ought to squeeze in here?

00:04:09.020 --> 00:04:10.020
 What?

00:04:10.020 --> 00:04:10.920
 Look, in the icebox.

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:12.720
 Here's half a can of love.

00:04:12.720 --> 00:04:14.080
 Why didn't I think of that before?

00:04:14.080 --> 00:04:14.920
 - Sure.

