 Homer, where'd you go?

00:09:42.540 --> 00:09:43.380
 Homer?

00:09:43.380 --> 00:09:44.220
 Yeah, what do you have, Henry?

00:09:44.220 --> 00:09:45.060
 Make it five.

00:09:45.060 --> 00:09:45.900
 Yes, sir.

00:09:45.900 --> 00:09:46.740
 Coming up.

00:09:46.740 --> 00:09:47.580
 Five what?

